CBRE, as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present 691 Pittwater Road, Dee Why. The property is a commercial freehold building which takes full advantage of its high exposure location along Pittwater Road within Dee Why Town Centre. Just moments from Dee Why Beach, B-Line bus services and public amenity, 691 Pittwater Road offers a flexible investment that capitalises on its premium location.

691 Pittwater Road, Dee Why benefits from the following key investment highlights:

• Floor area: 1,039sqm*
- Site area: 650sqm*
• Currently leased to The Commonwealth Bank of Australia. Lease terminates 1 October 2018
• Net rent of $271,065 per annum*
• 100% of outgoings paid by the tenant
- Flexible B4 Mixed use zoning allowing for residential flat buildings and shop top housing (apartments) (S.T.C.A)
- 24 metre height limit (S.T.C.A)
• Premium location within Dee Why Town Centre
• Metres from Dee Why Beach, B-Line bus stop, shops and dining options
• Short drive to Westfield Warringah Mall & new Northern Beaches Hospital

The property will be offered for sale via public auction on Tuesday, 31 July 2018 at 10:30am at AuctionWORKS.

*Approximate

For more information, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

CBRE as the exclusive sales agent is pleased to present, 32 Westminster Avenue, Dee Why.

+ DA Approved for 6 large 2 bedroom apartments plus 10 basement car spaces.
+ Site Area: 697.2sqm*
+ Approved GFA 592sqm*
+ Approved NSA 558sqm*
+ Perfectly designed 2 bedroom half-floor apartments with large open plan flowing floor plans enjoying three sides of natural light and only one common wall.
+ Existing improvements include a duplex with renovated 2 bedroom apartment and 3 bedroom apartment providing opportunity for holding income.
+ Beachside suburb with a strong demand for large apartments from buyers and tenants.
+ Lifestyle focused location moments to Dee Why Town Centre, shops, parks, Dee Why Beach, schools and public transport.
+ Easy Walk to Dee Why rapid B-Line bus stop, providing express services to Sydney CBD and greater Northern Beaches.
*Approx.
